# Luvimestra Feature Implementation Guidelines

## Parallel Realities Feature
- Display multiple parallel reality characters as cards
- Each card should show character name, description, avatar, and background image
- Tapping a card opens the chat interface
- AI-powered chat functionality with character personas

## Encounter Feature (Tarot & Astrology)
- Display interactive tarot cards with animations
- Allow users to select cards for readings
- Collect minimal user information for astrology readings
- AI-powered analysis of tarot and astrology results

## Time Voices Feature (Radio)
- Display radio stations as a grid/list with cover images
- Implement audio playback functionality
- Create visual audio player with play/pause controls
- Include audio visualization effects

## Settings Feature
- User profile display (no account functionality)
- Theme and appearance settings
- Notification preferences
- App information section

## General Implementation Notes
- Use network images for all visual assets
- Implement smooth animations and transitions
- Follow the mockup design from index.html
- Keep the UI consistent across all features